{
  "stem": "22892.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he grabbed a horse, and he was chasing me with a horse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I ran towards the first farm I've seen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was like a, a fence, a sm-- not very high fence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was-- it's a huge farm with a lot of straw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was freshly-- well, what am I tr-- the-- the-- there were a lot of fresh stacks of straw, that it's early in the fall, and it's harvest season.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I ran towards the far-- to that-- I got to that fence, and he was almost right there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I jumped over the fence, rolled over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I made a dive in the straw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was lots of straw, fresh straw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, and, and by the time he got off the horse, and he started climbing over that little fence, he came towards the area.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I could hear his foots-- feet on the straw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was starting looking and looking and going further away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, and, and he just couldn't-- I'm sure he couldn't understand what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I, I made-- you know, he just couldn't see me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then dogs were barking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Soon a stranger comes, dogs always bark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And people from that farmer-- I mean from that farm didn't know what the hell was going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I hear-- I hear them talk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It wasn't very clear, but I heard them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they, they don't know what's going on and they were looking and looking and looking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And this went on till lunchtime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Oh, the reason I was-- I knew it was lunchtime because then they start-- I don't know I used to know by what they would do, how they feed the, the chickens or whatever.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then things got quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That means he was gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
